name: Charlie
description: Charlie is a 10 year old Golden Retreiver male. He is energetic, has a big heart, and loves being around people.

inquiries.name: Dan
inquiries.comment: Charlie is one good looking dog. I'd like to adopt him!

name: Kelly
description: Kelly is a 7 year old Labrador Retreiver female. She loves to swim and to play outdoors. She is great with kids.

name: Murphy
description: Murphy is a 5 year old Pit Bull male. Despite his intimidating appearance, he is very kind and loves kids.

name: Shannon
description: Shannon is an 8 year old Labrador Retreiver female. She is full of energy and enjoys playing with other dogs.

name: Riley
description: Riley is a 6 year old Golden Retreiver male. He is very fond of swimming in the ocean, and he loves treats.

name: Kayla
description: Kayla is a 9 year old Doberman Pinscher female. She has a lot of energy for her age, and is great with children.

name: Gabe
description: Gabe is a 3 year old Cockapoo male. He is very affectionate, and enjoys going for long walks.

name: Cole
description: Cole despite his age, is extremley energentic, loving, and protective. He also loves warm weather.

name: Sam
description: Sam is a 4 year old Golden Retriever that was first discovered on the streets of Rome, Italy as a pup. She's shy at first but extremley friendly & loving with time.

name: Michael
description: Michael is a male, 2 year old Siberian Husky. He's best described as a gentle giant.

name: Leonardo
description: Leonardo is one of our more playful dogs. He absolutley loves being outdoors year-round & is also great with children.

name: Jade
description: Jade is the perfect dog for an older family/individual. She's very loving, laid-back, and loves to sleep.

name: Miley
description: Miley is one of our youngest dogs. She is extremley playful, loving, & full over energy 24/7.

name: Rolly
description: Rolly may seem a bit intimidating at first glace, but he's honestly one of the sweetest & most affectionate dogs around. Rolly is a real sweetheart.

name: Jack
description: Jack loves the kids! He loves to snuggle up, enjoys the outdoors, and loves to run, run, run.

name: Leah
description: For a  younger dog, Leah is surprisngly very low maintenance. She's very frindly, loving, and loves to get all the attention.

name: Mitch
description: Mitch lives for the outdoors. If you love the outdoors as well, Mitch will be the perfect companion for you.

name: Marsha
description: Marsha is the perfect dog for comforting you on your bad days, and making your good days even better. Marsha has a special knack for connecting with her owner on an emotinal level

name: Regina
description: Regina has a great heart & spirit. She loves to be spoiled and loved.

name: Brian
description: Brian is very quiet initially, but once he warms up to you, there's no stopping his little motor from running. Brian is very loving and great with all ages.

name: Pat
description: Pat easily has to be one of the most playful & affectionate dogs around. Even when you dont feel like playing Pat will find a way to make you play with her.

name: Leana
description: Leana wouldn't harm a fly, literally. She wants nothing but to keep her owner happy. Leana is the perfect dog for anyone.
